title: New Call of Duty Looks Terrible...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Modern Warfare 3, the 2023 title and not the one that came out over a decade ago and see just how little is finally changing for the "new" full-priced release. A rehash of maps from a decade ago and the worst spin on Zombies I've seen from this franchise is setting any potential hype I would have had completely out the window. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
